<p><strong>Greater Warpwave (Su)</strong> A creature struck by an izfiitar's bite or claw must succeed at a DC 31 Fortitude save or be affected by a greater warpwave. Roll 1d20 and consult the following list for exact effects on the creature. The save DC is Constitution-based.</p>
